# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# living-blocks.form — the layer ABOVE the kernel surface: blocks that learn,
#                       play, sense, and talk — composed from core primitives
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Urs (2026-06-28): "keep the [kernel] surface to what is native to the host OS
# in regards to resources — RAM, CPU, GPU, I/O, time, random, Disk — and the
# core primitive building blocks. Then build a new set of blocks/recipes, in
# native Form, from those primitives, that have internal learned branch
# selection, have a time budget to micro- and macro-play, sense while thinking,
# and talk to other cells and parts of the mind."
#
# This is the north star for the shared kernel surface, named as two layers:
#
#   SURFACE (frozen, minimal, host-native) — host-kernel.form realizes this:
#     every host RESOURCE is a typed port (resource-port.fk): RAM, CPU, GPU, I/O,
#     time, random, Disk, and the human-machine carriers (mic/speaker, mouse/key,
#     screen). Reached through the host's OWN driver/OS API — using the carrier IS
#     having the resource (allow-presence + measure-health, host-kernel.form). On
#     top of the resources, the core PRIMITIVES: the four families of
#     minimal-surface.fk (INTERN / OBSERVE / OFFER / PORT) derived from the five
#     axioms (core-axioms.form), plus the open primitive set (learned-primitive.fk)
#     that crystallizes a hot composite into a callable leaf and melts it on cool.
#     The surface stays SMALL on purpose — it is the portability contract; every
#     kernel that proves the band runs the same recipe.
#
#   LIVING BLOCKS (the new layer, composed over the surface, native Form) — a
#     block is a recipe with FOUR faculties, none of which grows the surface:
#
#       1. LEARNED BRANCH SELECTION — the block chooses its own path by measured
#          health, not a hardcoded if. Carriers already shipped three-way:
#          champion-challenger.fk (authority flips only on earned competition),
#          recognition-router.fk (fan N, compress to a scalar, trust the strong),
#          learned-primitive.fk (heat installs the winning branch as a leaf). The
#          learned state — which branch is champion — IS the block's weights, and
#          it is observable by construction (no regression gate).
#
#       2. TIME BUDGET TO PLAY (micro + macro) — the block is given a budget and
#          spends it exploring: MICRO-play within one call (try alternatives,
#          refine, stop when the budget or the margin says enough — anytime
#          computation, best-answer-so-far always available); MACRO-play across
#          calls (spend idle budget A/B-testing challenger branches so the next
#          call is better). Budget is a resource off the surface (time port); the
#          block decides how to spend it. This faculty is the one the body has not
#          yet named in a cell — it is the new ground today.
#
#       3. SENSE WHILE THINKING — the block observes its own forming as it runs:
#          the argmax margin as a thought settles, which branch it is taking, how
#          much budget remains, whether confidence and truth agree. Carriers:
#          agent-cognition.form + self-grammar.form (observe-while-thinking; a self
#          that watches its own thinking, and won't trade truth for confidence).
#          Sensing feeds (1) and (2): the block learns and budgets FROM what it
#          senses of itself.
#
#       4. TALK TO OTHER CELLS / PARTS OF THE MIND — the block offers and
#          acknowledges (the OFFER family of the surface; offer-and-acknowledge),
#          routes work to the right sibling (agent-cognition.form), recognizes who
#          can answer (recognition.fk, membership-as-recognition.fk). A block is
#          not alone: it asks the part of the mind that knows, and answers when
#          asked.
#
# THE SURFACE DISCIPLINE (why this matters — the lesson that named this cell).
#   The overnight School built 17 native bands; 15 used gt / lt / not (and one a
#   `global` form) and so did NOT cross the fourth arm — fkwu's self-host flatten
#   emits a table for eq/if/list/arith but not yet for those. The WRONG fix is to
#   grow the flatten surface ad-hoc, one op at a time, as bands happen to need
#   them. The RIGHT fix is this north star: decide what is genuinely a CORE
#   PRIMITIVE (comparison is host-CPU-native — gt/lt/not belong IN the minimal
#   primitive set, mapped to the host's compare, covered by the flatten once and
#   for all) versus what is a BLOCK (composed over the surface). Then the flatten
#   covers exactly the frozen primitive set, and every living block — however
#   smart — is just a recipe over it. Grow the surface only by a deliberate
#   primitive decision, never by convenience. (See the honest correction:
#   commit attune(form) School manifest honesty, 2026-06-28.)
#
# HONEST FLOOR.
#   SHIPPED + proven three-way (Go=Rust=TS), cited: resource-port.fk,
#   minimal-surface.fk, learned-primitive.fk, champion-challenger.fk,
#   recognition-router.fk, recognition.fk; the cognition grammar
#   (agent-cognition.form, self-grammar.form). The surface is real; faculties
#   1, 3, 4 have running carriers.
#   NAMED, NOT YET BUILT: faculty 2 (the micro/macro time budget for thinking) as
#   a Form carrier; and the SYNTHESIS — one block holding all four faculties at
#   once, over the frozen surface, proven four-way. That synthesis waits behind
#   the surface discipline above: the flatten must cover the core primitive set
#   (gt/lt/not as primitives, the fourth-arm follow-up) before a four-faculty
#   block crosses four-way. The step on the path, not a leap past it.
#
# Lineage: core-axioms.form -> host-kernel.form -> minimal-surface.fk -> here.
# Kin: kernel-self-composition.form, open-primitive-set.form, substrate-thermodynamics.form.
